r.net/articles/2015-04-26-call-of-duty-black-ops-3-pc-requirements-revealed|title=Call of Duty: Black Ops 3 PC requirements revealed|last=Robinson|first=Martin|date=April 26, 2015|accessdate=April 28, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2018 || ''[[Call of Duty: Black Ops 4]]'' || Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4, Xbox One\n|}\n\n===Assistant Developer===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Game !! Platform(s) !! Developer(s)\n|-\n| 2011 ||''[[Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3]]''\n| Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 3, Xbox 360, Wii|| rowspan=\"4\" |[[Infinity Ward]]\n|-\n|2013\n|''[[Call of Duty: Ghosts]]''\n|Microsoft Windows, Playstation 3, Playstation 4, Xbox 360, Xbox One, Wii U\n|-\n|2016||''[[Call of Duty: Infinite Warfare]]''\n|Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4, Xbox One\n|}\n\n===Ports===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Game !! Platform(s) !! Developer(s)\n|-\n| rowspan=2 | 2000 || ''[[Tony Hawk's Pro Skater]]'' || rowspan=3 | Dreamcast || rowspan=3 | [[Neversoft]]\n|-\n| ''[[Tony Hawk's Pro Skater 2]]''\n|-\n| 2001 || ''[[Spider-Man (2000 video game)|Spider-Man]]''\n|-\n| 2009 || ''[[Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare#Retail versions|Call of Duty: Modern Warfare: Reflex]]'' || rowspan=2 | Wii || rowspan=3 | [[Infinity Ward]]\n|-\n| 2011 || ''[[Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3]]''\n|-\n| 2013 || ''[[Call of Duty: Ghosts]]'' || Wii U\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.treyarch.com/ Official website]\n\n{{Activision}}\n{{Call of Duty series}}\n\n{{Use mdy dates|date=October 2012}}\n\n[[Category:Activision]]\n[[Category:Companies based in Santa Monica, California]]\n[[Category:Video game companies established in 1996]]\n[[Category:1996 establishments in California]]\n[[Category:Former Vivendi subsidiaries]]\n[[Category:Video game companies of the United States]]\n[[Category:Video game development companies]]\n[[Category:2001 mergers and acquisitions]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox company\n| name = Treyarch\n| logo = Treyarch 